<i>A local attorney, many are now calling,
the Bloody Bride was arrested today</i>

03:40.915 --> 03:43.501
<i>on the charge of murdering her
would-be husband.</i>

03:43.541 --> 03:45.622
<i>Respected jurors were
startled this morning</i>

03:45.662 --> 03:48.668
<i>by the sight of Renatta Hill
rushing past them,</i>

03:48.708 --> 03:51.292
<i>her white gown covered in blood.</i>

03:51.292 --> 03:54.189
“Bloody Bride”, like that
won't taint the jury pool.

03:54.229 --> 03:57.618
As I'm sure, you're aware
Mr Shore is representing Ms Hill.

03:57.658 --> 04:01.054
Please refrain from
speaking to the press.

04:01.054 --> 04:03.035
The firm will comment when appropriate.

04:03.075 --> 04:05.603
If anybody needs me,
I'll be on my cell.

04:05.643 --> 04:06.852
And where are you going?

04:06.892 --> 04:08.075
Rehab.

04:08.075 --> 04:09.972
I said something bad about
the Jews, I don't know what,

04:10.012 --> 04:12.079
but Bethany has left me over it.

04:12.119 --> 04:17.196
Anyway, I recognize that I have issues
I need to examine within my soul.

04:17.196 --> 04:20.628
I'm getting treatment. And with
the help of family and friends

04:20.668 --> 04:23.133
I shall make a full recovery.

